basic.Source: Synthetic construct(derived from measles virus(MV) fusion (F) protein)
basic.Target Organism: [Ref.8700906]measles virus(MeV):protection of HEp2 cell from viral cytopathic effect(CPE)(EC50=1.5 μg/ml);inhibition of cell-cell fusion in HEp2 cell(EC50=0.068 μg/ml);Human parainfluenza virus type 3(HPIV-3):inhibition of cell-cell fusion in HEp2 cell(EC50>25 μg/ml);Respiratory syncytial virus(RSV):inhibition of cell-cell fusion in HEp2 cell(EC50>25 μg/ml);HIV-1 LAI:inhibition of cell-cell fusion in HEp2 cell(EC50>50 μg/ml).
